WEBVTT

00:16.690 --> 00:20.400
[Taiji Hall]

00:19.510 --> 00:20.870
Lord Woo has arrived!

00:22.800 --> 00:24.160
Lord Wu has arrived!

00:25.070 --> 00:26.870
Vice Minister Fang has arrived!

00:42.790 --> 00:44.750
Earlier at the Golden Celestial Hall,

00:44.750 --> 00:46.710
I only caught a glimpse of you, General.

00:46.710 --> 00:49.790
I greatly admire your feat in slaying

00:49.790 --> 00:51.200
the rebel Lord Changxin.

00:51.290 --> 00:52.360
It's an honor to be here with you tonight.

00:52.360 --> 00:54.820
Let me propose a toast
to you first, General.

00:57.790 --> 00:58.350
Please.

01:01.810 --> 01:02.880
General, you can really hold your liquor!

01:02.880 --> 01:03.580
Indeed.

01:03.600 --> 01:04.150
Indeed.

01:04.920 --> 01:06.630
General Fan, you're young and promising,

01:06.630 --> 01:07.590
renowned far and wide,

01:07.590 --> 01:09.190
and striking in appearance.

01:09.760 --> 01:11.230
It's truly remarkable that you managed to

01:11.230 --> 01:12.480
kill Lord Changxin.

01:12.480 --> 01:12.710
Yes, indeed.

01:12.710 --> 01:14.950
Allow me to toast you as well, General.

01:18.740 --> 01:20.289
If this keeps up,

01:20.450 --> 01:23.450
that butcher woman will surely
make a fool of herself.

01:24.200 --> 01:25.070
Never mind her.

01:26.630 --> 01:29.289
Why hasn't
the Eldest Young Master arrived yet?

01:29.460 --> 01:32.620
[Action Through Inaction]

01:31.530 --> 01:32.400
Another toast to you, General Fan.

01:32.400 --> 01:33.840
Grand Tutor.

01:33.840 --> 01:35.280
I heard your heart condition
has flared up recently, Master.

01:35.280 --> 01:36.350
Are you feeling better now?

01:36.350 --> 01:37.229
Much better.

01:37.229 --> 01:38.479
I've been quite worried, Master.

01:38.479 --> 01:39.680
What a remarkable capacity for drink!

01:39.680 --> 01:41.479
That butcher woman
throws her weight around—

01:41.479 --> 01:43.610
we've suffered unbearably under her.

01:46.640 --> 01:48.070
Let's not just watch here. Come on.

01:48.070 --> 01:49.920
I'll drink a few cups with you all.

01:49.920 --> 01:50.870
Good things come in pairs.

01:50.870 --> 01:53.509
-We must enjoy ourselves tonight.
-Let me propose another toast to you.

01:53.509 --> 01:54.070
Cheers.

02:07.760 --> 02:10.820
Isn't His Majesty hosting today's banquet
in my honor?

02:11.430 --> 02:13.750
You all belong to
Prime Minister Wei's faction,

02:13.750 --> 02:15.150
so why do you keep

02:15.150 --> 02:17.190
offering toasts only to
the Flower-Crowned General?

02:17.190 --> 02:18.079
Could it be

02:18.520 --> 02:20.450
that you look down on this Marquis?

02:22.190 --> 02:23.520
You jest, Your Lordship.

02:23.520 --> 02:25.030
General Fan arrived first,

02:25.030 --> 02:27.160
so we simply wished to liven things up.

02:27.620 --> 02:30.880
Allow me to toast Your Lordship
on your triumphant return.

02:38.400 --> 02:39.260
Your Lordship,

02:39.440 --> 02:41.210
we serve in the same court.

02:41.630 --> 02:43.000
Why did you do that?

02:43.750 --> 02:45.680
You're Vice Minister Fang, right?

02:45.870 --> 02:47.670
As the Vice Minister of Revenue,

02:48.000 --> 02:50.280
you were responsible for grain supplies
to the border, right?

02:50.280 --> 02:51.680
And if I were?

02:51.960 --> 02:54.280
You nearly caused civil unrest in Jizhou.

02:54.280 --> 02:56.280
I haven't held you accountable yet,

02:56.430 --> 02:57.750
and here you are
acting like someone of importance.

02:57.750 --> 02:58.360
You...

02:59.520 --> 03:01.800
Tonight's banquet is held
in Your Lordship's honor.

03:01.800 --> 03:03.240
Let's not discuss official business.

03:03.240 --> 03:05.000
Vice Minister Fang,
you have wine all over yourself.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.560
Please step away and rest a moment.

03:06.540 --> 03:12.940
[Action Through Inaction]

03:06.840 --> 03:08.170
Your Lordship, please.

03:09.240 --> 03:11.500
The Prime Minister will arrive shortly.

03:12.840 --> 03:13.670
Let's go.

03:13.770 --> 03:14.710
Excuse us, Your Lordship.

03:14.710 --> 03:15.960
This is outrageous!

03:17.630 --> 03:19.520
Grand Tutor, come on. Let me fill it up.

03:19.520 --> 03:21.710
The real show has just begun.

03:22.430 --> 03:25.420
Let's sit back and watch.

03:26.590 --> 03:29.150
I was worried
you might actually come to blows.

03:29.150 --> 03:31.880
You think too highly of
those corrupt officials.

03:32.110 --> 03:34.570
They're all despicable at heart,

03:34.600 --> 03:36.400
yet all know they're beneath me.

03:36.400 --> 03:38.660
They wouldn't dare cause a scene openly.

03:40.630 --> 03:43.150
Don't worry.
I'll leave the banquet in a bit.

03:43.150 --> 03:45.350
Gongsun will assist me from the inside.

03:48.420 --> 03:49.050
Sit.

03:52.280 --> 03:55.340
His Majesty has arrived!

03:55.630 --> 03:58.470
-We respectfully welcome Your Majesty.
-We respectfully welcome Your Majesty.

03:58.470 --> 04:00.670
We respectfully welcome Your Majesty.

04:00.800 --> 04:02.120
Grand Tutor, you've recovered.

04:02.120 --> 04:03.180
That's wonderful!

04:04.000 --> 04:05.690
Thank you for your concern, Your Majesty.

04:05.370 --> 04:08.940
[Action Through Inaction]

04:05.800 --> 04:07.400
This old subject is ashamed.

04:08.000 --> 04:11.460
Prime Minister Wei, it's been a lot
for you these past few days.

04:11.750 --> 04:13.000
I always do my duty diligently.

04:13.000 --> 04:14.310
I don't find it taxing.

04:14.590 --> 04:15.630
But you, Grand Tutor,

04:15.630 --> 04:17.040
you must take care of your health.

04:17.040 --> 04:19.360
Balance work and rest.

04:21.190 --> 04:22.720
Thank you for your concern.

04:23.600 --> 04:25.920
Both of you are pillars of the state.

04:26.040 --> 04:28.430
Today is a day of double joy.

04:28.510 --> 04:29.720
I'm very pleased.

04:31.560 --> 04:34.120
In quelling the rebellion in Chongzhou,

04:34.120 --> 04:35.600
the Marquis of Wu'an
risked his life repeatedly

04:35.600 --> 04:37.060
and rendered great merit.

04:37.490 --> 04:45.659
[Action Through Inaction]

04:37.510 --> 04:40.360
The four prefectures of the northwest
have remained secure

04:40.360 --> 04:41.750
thanks to his defense.

04:42.480 --> 04:45.800
Therefore, I hereby grant
the Marquis of Wu'an the Longquan Sword.

04:45.800 --> 04:48.430
This sword was forged
by the founding emperor of our dynasty.

04:48.430 --> 04:51.360
With it, one may strike down
foolish rulers above...

04:55.159 --> 04:56.560
and execute treacherous officials below.

04:56.560 --> 04:57.960
It's a token of my regard.

04:59.870 --> 05:00.560
Present it.

05:06.950 --> 05:08.310
This Longquan Sword...

05:11.750 --> 05:13.610
truly lives up to its reputation.

05:17.950 --> 05:20.150
To strike down foolish rulers above...

05:22.240 --> 05:24.640
and execute treacherous officials below.

05:31.390 --> 05:32.730
It is a fine sword.

05:34.750 --> 05:36.480
However, I'm devoted to the realm

05:36.480 --> 05:37.940
and unwavering in my duty.

05:38.240 --> 05:39.970
This sword is far too precious—

05:40.620 --> 05:43.280
no one but Your Majesty
is worthy of wielding it.

05:49.000 --> 05:50.630
Marquis of Wu'an, your loyalty

05:50.630 --> 05:51.720
is known to me.

05:52.950 --> 05:54.480
At today's palace banquet,

05:55.000 --> 05:57.190
let us all drink until dawn!

05:57.240 --> 05:58.860
-Thank you, Your Majesty.
-Thank you, Your Majesty.

05:58.860 --> 06:00.590
I need to step away for a moment.

06:01.630 --> 06:03.680
His Majesty takes his leave.

06:04.720 --> 06:06.730
-We respectfully send off Your Majesty.
-We respectfully send off Your Majesty.

06:06.730 --> 06:11.250
[Action Through Inaction]

06:08.240 --> 06:09.040
Your Majesty?

06:10.390 --> 06:11.190
Your Majesty.

06:12.020 --> 06:13.380
Your Highness,

06:13.560 --> 06:16.430
Consort Dowager An has specially sent me

06:16.480 --> 06:17.950
to remind Your Highness

06:18.430 --> 06:20.760
that the palace banquet is about to begin.

06:20.830 --> 06:22.750
Please do not be late.

06:28.830 --> 06:29.920
Please forgive me, Your Highness!

06:29.920 --> 06:31.120
I didn't mean to!

06:32.610 --> 06:34.630
You... You wretched maid!

06:34.630 --> 06:35.430
It's fine.

06:37.950 --> 06:40.400
Today is a celebration banquet hosted
by my brother for the Marquis of Wu'an.

06:40.400 --> 06:41.950
It's not appropriate to lose one's temper.

06:41.950 --> 06:42.520
You...

06:42.540 --> 06:43.370
You may leave.

06:43.510 --> 06:44.120
Yes!

06:45.070 --> 06:45.720
You...

06:47.720 --> 06:51.980
It was my lax discipline.
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

06:53.010 --> 06:54.600
I have to go back and change.

06:54.630 --> 06:56.790
I assume
the Marquis of Wu'an and my brother...

06:56.790 --> 06:58.190
won't take offense.

06:58.310 --> 06:59.950
W-Well...

07:01.190 --> 07:02.430
Your Highness!

07:05.680 --> 07:08.240
His Majesty is waiting for you!

07:09.510 --> 07:11.000
Xie Zheng, Wei Yan—

07:11.000 --> 07:12.040
that uncle and nephew
are cut from the same cloth!

07:12.040 --> 07:13.630
Neither of them has ever taken me,
the Emperor, seriously!

07:13.630 --> 07:14.760
They deserve to die!

07:15.510 --> 07:16.910
They both deserve to die!

07:18.510 --> 07:19.720
In that case,

07:20.040 --> 07:22.370
don't blame me
for not giving you a chance!

09:07.810 --> 09:13.040
[Pursuit of Jade]

09:13.180 --> 09:15.720
[Episode 37]

09:29.330 --> 09:34.510
[Action Through Inaction]

09:29.840 --> 09:32.270
My dear subjects,
the atmosphere isn't right!

09:32.270 --> 09:33.840
Play on, and dance on!

09:34.000 --> 09:34.630
Drink up!

09:41.880 --> 09:42.360
Grand Tutor!

09:42.360 --> 09:42.870
Your Majesty.

09:42.870 --> 09:44.730
Does our country still rely on me?

09:44.750 --> 09:45.670
Of course.

09:45.910 --> 09:47.910
The prosperity of our country
for generations to come

09:47.910 --> 09:50.520
rests entirely on
Your Majesty's divine brilliance!

09:47.980 --> 09:54.620
[Action Through Inaction]

09:50.600 --> 09:52.690
What would this realm do without me,

09:52.720 --> 09:53.720
wouldn't you say?

09:53.790 --> 09:54.750
Yes, yes, yes.

09:56.910 --> 09:59.390
Drunks are all alike,
no matter their rank.

09:59.450 --> 10:00.750
The way the Emperor gets drunk

10:00.750 --> 10:02.150
and boasts—

10:02.720 --> 10:04.360
it's just like Mr. Zhao.

10:06.630 --> 10:07.760
Prime Minister Wei!

10:11.360 --> 10:12.000
Gong...

10:14.750 --> 10:16.010
We've found the woman,

10:16.360 --> 10:18.080
and the Princess Royal
had her brought out.

10:18.080 --> 10:20.210
She's been placed in Qingyuan Palace.

10:20.480 --> 10:21.560
Not gonna lie—

10:21.870 --> 10:24.260
this look actually suits you.

10:27.600 --> 10:29.060
Thank you, Your Lordship.

10:30.550 --> 10:31.440
Little eunuch.

10:32.430 --> 10:34.630
Bring that plate of pastries over here.

10:37.960 --> 10:38.690
Yes, my lord.

10:43.390 --> 10:45.150
My subjects, drink your fill.

10:49.960 --> 10:50.550
You...

10:55.510 --> 10:56.600
Please forgive me, Your Lordship.

10:56.600 --> 10:58.530
Please forgive me, Your Lordship!

11:03.360 --> 11:05.120
Marquis of Wu'an, are you alright?

11:05.120 --> 11:05.910
I'm fine.

11:06.160 --> 11:07.810
You stupid eunuch.

11:07.960 --> 11:09.720
How dare you offend my Marquis of Wu'an!

11:09.720 --> 11:11.630
Guards! Take him away and punish him!

11:10.330 --> 11:14.060
[Action Through Inaction]

11:11.630 --> 11:13.080
-Yes, Your Majesty.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

11:13.080 --> 11:14.880
Your Majesty, please calm down.

11:15.150 --> 11:16.440
At a palace banquet like this,

11:16.440 --> 11:18.100
it's better not to shed blood,

11:18.320 --> 11:20.250
lest it spoil Your Majesty's mood.

11:21.720 --> 11:23.360
You're so magnanimous.

11:24.120 --> 11:24.910
You may go.

11:24.660 --> 11:26.480
[Action Through Inaction]

11:25.720 --> 11:26.790
Alright.

11:27.030 --> 11:29.000
Since the Marquis has pleaded for you,
you stupid eunuch,

11:29.000 --> 11:30.330
thank him immediately.

11:31.200 --> 11:32.150
Thank you, Your Majesty.

11:32.150 --> 11:33.200
Thank you, Your Lordship.

11:33.200 --> 11:34.790
What are you just standing there for?

11:34.790 --> 11:37.120
Escort the Marquis to change his clothes!

11:37.670 --> 11:38.390
Yes.

11:41.030 --> 11:42.430
Thank you, Your Majesty.

11:47.780 --> 11:50.800
[Action Through Inaction]

11:57.910 --> 11:59.360
The Emperor today...

11:59.830 --> 12:01.630
seems a bit overexcited.

12:07.120 --> 12:08.000
Cheers!

12:24.270 --> 12:25.930
Prime Minister, please wait!

12:28.120 --> 12:30.180
I heard that during the Battle of Lucheng,

12:30.180 --> 12:33.310
it was thanks to
your timely dispatch of grain supplies.

12:33.510 --> 12:34.870
You brilliantly str...

12:35.910 --> 12:37.710
strategized behind the scenes.

12:37.910 --> 12:39.440
I, on behalf of...

12:41.270 --> 12:42.830
the fallen border soldiers

12:43.600 --> 12:45.550
and the wrongfully dead border civilians,

12:45.550 --> 12:46.550
offer you a toast.

12:54.240 --> 12:55.120
Fan Changyu!

12:55.240 --> 12:57.240
Are you toasting or being insolent?

12:57.480 --> 12:58.390
Go on.

12:58.870 --> 13:00.150
Toasting, of course.

13:01.080 --> 13:03.290
If not for our Prime Minister's help,

13:03.470 --> 13:05.450
[Supreme Order and Benevolent Governance]

13:03.600 --> 13:05.060
Lucheng would likely have

13:05.750 --> 13:08.650
become another Jinzhou,
just as it did 17 years ago,

13:09.670 --> 13:11.030
with no reinforcements

13:11.390 --> 13:12.720
and no supplies.

13:13.590 --> 13:15.390
By then, Old General He would not

13:15.630 --> 13:17.550
have been the only one to fall.

13:17.550 --> 13:21.010
The Marquis of Wu'an would've met
the same fate as General Xie—

13:22.270 --> 13:24.800
dying wretchedly,
strung up on the city walls

13:25.200 --> 13:27.420
with his body torn open by the enemy.

13:27.910 --> 13:29.600
I'm just a butcher.

13:29.670 --> 13:32.410
My end likely wouldn't compare to...

13:33.390 --> 13:35.890
the big traitor Wei Qilin.

13:36.310 --> 13:37.460
So tell me—

13:38.120 --> 13:39.780
doesn't that deserve a toast?

13:41.670 --> 13:43.210
As an official,

13:43.480 --> 13:44.940
I have a clear conscience.

13:48.960 --> 13:50.440
However, General Fan,

13:51.630 --> 13:53.780
you truly are no match for Wei Qilin.

14:16.480 --> 14:17.410
Prime Minister.

14:17.440 --> 14:18.440
Where is the Marquis of Wu'an?

14:18.440 --> 14:19.860
His Lordship said he needed to sober up

14:19.860 --> 14:21.990
and went towards the Imperial Garden.

14:22.270 --> 14:23.510
Find him immediately

14:23.510 --> 14:24.710
and report back to me.

14:25.120 --> 14:25.720
Yes.

14:26.750 --> 14:27.630
General Fan!

14:31.200 --> 14:32.600
I, too, offer you a toast!

14:35.670 --> 14:38.530
And to all my subjects,
thank you for your hard work.

14:38.960 --> 14:40.720
Since I ascended the throne,

14:40.790 --> 14:42.670
fortunately, you civil
and military officials have united

14:42.670 --> 14:43.840
and worked in harmony to uphold the realm.

14:43.840 --> 14:46.440
Only thus does our country
enjoy peace today,

14:46.750 --> 14:49.480
and I can say I've honored
my ancestors' legacy.

14:50.080 --> 14:52.000
I dare not call myself a wise ruler,

14:52.000 --> 14:53.090
but tonight,

14:53.240 --> 14:55.720
all my subjects,
for the peace of our realm,

14:55.720 --> 14:57.450
let us drink this cup together!

14:58.790 --> 15:01.030
-Your Majesty is wise!
-Your Majesty is wise!

15:01.030 --> 15:03.240
-Your Majesty is a wise ruler!
-Your Majesty is a wise ruler!

15:03.240 --> 15:07.270
-Your Majesty is wise!
-Your Majesty is a wise ruler!

15:08.960 --> 15:10.960
What an incompetent emperor.

15:14.390 --> 15:16.850
Just as despicable as his father.

15:38.670 --> 15:39.840
You're finally here.

15:39.840 --> 15:41.100
I've brought her here.

15:42.030 --> 15:43.080
Your Highness,

15:43.200 --> 15:45.060
the osmanthus is blooming.

15:45.270 --> 15:46.320
Your Highness,

15:46.630 --> 15:48.340
the osmanthus is blooming.

15:48.910 --> 15:50.550
It wasn't easy to bring her here

15:50.550 --> 15:51.840
from the Cold Palace.

15:52.510 --> 15:53.360
Your Highness,

15:53.360 --> 15:54.320
fire.

15:54.440 --> 15:56.080
Since that fire years ago,

15:56.080 --> 15:58.390
people in the palace
have avoided this place.

15:58.390 --> 16:00.320
So it's safer to hide her here.

16:01.480 --> 16:03.130
But she's completely...

16:03.440 --> 16:04.670
delirious—

16:04.720 --> 16:06.080
rambling incoherently,

16:06.080 --> 16:07.240
making no sense at all.

16:07.240 --> 16:08.520
Fire,

16:08.750 --> 16:09.790
Your Highness.

16:10.390 --> 16:11.440
Your Highness...

16:14.200 --> 16:15.510
General Wei?

16:16.550 --> 16:18.240
Why have you returned?

16:18.240 --> 16:19.750
Her Highness has told you to run!

16:19.750 --> 16:20.630
Run!

16:20.630 --> 16:22.440
Run! Run!

16:23.240 --> 16:24.200
Fire!

16:24.390 --> 16:25.150
Fire!

16:25.600 --> 16:26.390
Fire!

16:26.750 --> 16:27.630
Fire...

16:28.630 --> 16:29.890
Who is "Her Highness"?

16:31.870 --> 16:32.800
Her Highness...

16:33.600 --> 16:35.060
Her Highness is pregnant.

16:35.840 --> 16:37.870
Your Majesty, you cannot beat her!

16:37.870 --> 16:40.130
Her Highness and the child will both die!

16:42.960 --> 16:44.490
The osmanthus is blooming.

16:44.870 --> 16:46.400
The osmanthus is blooming.

16:48.510 --> 16:50.000
It was Consort Virtue of the Qi clan.

16:50.000 --> 16:51.080
It smells so fragrant.

16:51.080 --> 16:52.280
This Qingyuan Palace

16:52.360 --> 16:54.240
was formerly Consort Virtue's palace.

16:54.240 --> 16:57.040
Many osmanthus trees
were planted here back then.

16:57.360 --> 16:58.200
Osmanthus...

16:58.510 --> 16:59.370
Your Highness!

17:00.000 --> 17:00.870
Osmanthus!

17:02.030 --> 17:02.890
Your Highness!

17:05.109 --> 17:07.240
I want to make incense with osmanthus.

17:09.829 --> 17:12.550
It smells so fragrant.
Who lit the incense?

17:12.640 --> 17:14.700
Who has lit incense for Her Highness?

17:21.109 --> 17:22.240
We've walked into a trap.

17:22.240 --> 17:23.369
Don't breathe it in.

17:24.160 --> 17:25.829
Marquis of Wu'an,

17:26.069 --> 17:30.110
you and that maid have already been
affected by an aphrodisiac!

17:30.880 --> 17:32.400
No matter what,

17:32.400 --> 17:36.200
you won't escape the charge of indecency
within the imperial harem!

17:36.310 --> 17:38.030
If you know what's good for you,

17:38.030 --> 17:39.680
surrender immediately!

17:40.200 --> 17:41.820
As long as you obey,

17:41.920 --> 17:43.070
His Majesty

17:43.070 --> 17:46.790
will surely spare your life!

17:54.640 --> 17:56.830
Marquis of Wu'an, oh, Marquis of Wu'an.

17:56.830 --> 17:59.030
No matter how brave and valiant you are,

17:59.110 --> 18:00.960
you won't escape—

18:00.960 --> 18:04.350
you're trapped like a rat!

18:11.110 --> 18:12.640
General Fan! Help!

18:12.720 --> 18:15.030
Someone must have discovered
the Princess Royal hiding that woman.

18:15.030 --> 18:17.200
She originally asked me to guard
near Qingyuan Palace,

18:17.200 --> 18:18.510
but shortly after the Marquis of Wu'an
went in,

18:18.510 --> 18:20.200
Li Xiang surrounded the palace
with his men.

18:20.200 --> 18:21.880
So I rushed here to report!

18:23.350 --> 18:24.790
I'll go to Qingyuan Palace.

18:24.790 --> 18:25.750
You go find Consort Dowager An.

18:25.750 --> 18:26.480
But Her Highness said

18:26.480 --> 18:28.830
Consort Dowager An
must not know about this!

18:28.830 --> 18:31.400
I'm afraid something terrible
is about to happen.

18:31.400 --> 18:32.790
Only Consort Dowager An can
take control of the situation.

18:32.790 --> 18:33.310
Go.

18:33.310 --> 18:34.000
Yes.

18:47.110 --> 18:48.160
Quick! Get him!

18:48.160 --> 18:49.760
All of you, attack together!

19:15.200 --> 19:17.670
Isn't he already poisoned?

19:17.880 --> 19:20.000
Why can he still fight like that?

20:27.590 --> 20:28.190
Yan Zheng?

20:28.790 --> 20:29.510
Yan Zheng!

20:30.030 --> 20:30.680
Yan Zheng!

20:31.240 --> 20:31.920
Get up!

20:43.820 --> 20:44.650
Yan Zheng.

20:45.790 --> 20:47.180
What happened?

20:47.640 --> 20:48.720
Changyu...

20:54.310 --> 20:55.570
Why are you burning up?

21:04.310 --> 21:05.970
Your hand—how did it get hurt?

21:06.440 --> 21:07.490
Changyu...

21:15.830 --> 21:17.230
It's too dangerous here.

21:31.310 --> 21:32.000
Come here!

21:50.480 --> 21:51.070
Hurry!

21:51.640 --> 21:53.200
Go seal the palace gates immediately!

21:53.200 --> 21:54.590
An assassin has broken into
the Imperial Garden!

21:54.590 --> 21:55.250
-Yes!
-Yes!

22:09.440 --> 22:10.270
Your Majesty,

22:10.750 --> 22:12.750
this old subject offers you a toast.

22:14.750 --> 22:15.480
Grand Tutor!

22:16.310 --> 22:17.440
Prime Minister Wei?

22:20.240 --> 22:21.930
Come on, my subjects.

22:28.200 --> 22:30.830
Where are the Marquis of Wu'an
and the Flower-Crowned General?

22:30.830 --> 22:32.160
Why have they both gone?

22:32.310 --> 22:34.070
Your Majesty,
something terrible has happened!

22:34.070 --> 22:34.870
Your Majesty!

22:35.400 --> 22:37.400
The Marquis of Wu'an,
in a drunken disgrace,

22:37.400 --> 22:38.830
has actually seized a palace maid

22:38.830 --> 22:40.490
and attempted to violate her!

22:40.680 --> 22:42.070
This servant tried to stop him

22:42.070 --> 22:45.330
b-but was beaten and thrown out
by the Marquis!

22:45.440 --> 22:46.270
Insolent.

22:47.160 --> 22:48.920
Framing an important court official—

22:48.920 --> 22:50.720
do you know the penalty for that?

22:51.310 --> 22:52.640
I saw it with my own eyes.

22:52.920 --> 22:55.120
I wouldn't dare fabricate such a thing!

22:55.640 --> 22:56.510
Your Majesty,

22:56.960 --> 22:59.920
perhaps there is some misunderstanding.

23:00.480 --> 23:03.750
We'd better go see for ourselves.

23:03.750 --> 23:05.410
You're right, Grand Tutor Li.

23:07.830 --> 23:09.160
You wretched slave,

23:09.480 --> 23:11.480
how dare you frame my loyal general?

23:12.270 --> 23:13.270
My subjects!

23:14.510 --> 23:15.590
-Yes, Your Majesty.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

23:15.590 --> 23:17.110
Come with me to have a look!

23:17.160 --> 23:19.420
-Yes, Your Majesty.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

23:31.920 --> 23:34.520
Prime Minister Wei,
aren't you coming with me?

24:10.030 --> 24:11.590
I have urgent matters to report
to His Majesty.

24:11.590 --> 24:12.510
The situation is critical.

24:12.510 --> 24:13.510
Do not stop me.

24:13.510 --> 24:15.030
Lord Li, the palace banquet has begun.

24:15.030 --> 24:16.350
No entry without a decree.

24:16.350 --> 24:18.270
Violators will be punished
according to palace rules.

24:18.270 --> 24:19.550
We're just following orders.

24:19.550 --> 24:21.080
Please forgive us, Lord Li.

24:21.150 --> 24:23.720
[Waist token]

24:21.720 --> 24:24.000
This is the palace pass
His Majesty bestowed upon my family.

24:24.000 --> 24:25.000
I'm among those invited!

24:25.000 --> 24:26.800
Does even this not permit entry?

24:27.030 --> 24:28.260
Go search over there!

24:28.440 --> 24:29.510
Go!

24:30.780 --> 24:32.310
There, there, and over there!

24:32.310 --> 24:33.920
Search everywhere carefully!

24:33.920 --> 24:36.030
You useless idiots!

24:36.030 --> 24:38.140
There are a bunch of you,

24:38.170 --> 24:39.820
and you still can't find him?

24:40.100 --> 24:41.190
Search carefully!

24:42.000 --> 24:44.860
Head Eunuch Li, bad news!
There's a fire over there!

24:48.500 --> 24:49.510
Oh no.

24:49.680 --> 24:51.540
The hunter may become the hunted.

24:53.400 --> 24:54.720
Why are you just standing there?

24:54.720 --> 24:56.150
Can't you see the fire?

24:56.270 --> 24:59.400
This must be the Marquis of Wu'an
trying to destroy the evidence!

24:59.400 --> 25:01.240
Go put out the fire! Go!

25:01.240 --> 25:01.900
-Yes!
-Yes!

25:07.330 --> 25:11.900
[Qingyuan Palace]

25:12.640 --> 25:13.480
Well...

25:13.830 --> 25:16.070
How on earth did such a great fire
break out all of a sudden?

25:16.070 --> 25:16.830
Your Majesty,

25:16.830 --> 25:17.880
an attendant heard

25:17.880 --> 25:19.440
a palace maid cry out,
"licentious villain."

25:19.440 --> 25:20.640
By the time I arrived,

25:20.750 --> 25:21.440
I saw...

25:23.440 --> 25:24.800
Who did you see?

25:25.510 --> 25:28.370
I saw... the Marquis of Wu'an
fleeing from the hall.

25:28.440 --> 25:29.750
He even injured others.

25:29.750 --> 25:31.350
Head Eunuch Li has taken men to chase him.

25:31.350 --> 25:32.590
He escaped?

25:32.590 --> 25:34.110
How could you let him escape?

25:34.110 --> 25:34.910
Your Majesty!

25:36.940 --> 25:38.880
Xie Zheng has not only defiled
the imperial harem

25:38.880 --> 25:40.030
but also tried to destroy the evidence.

25:40.030 --> 25:41.200
He must be arrested immediately.

25:41.200 --> 25:43.510
If he resists, kill him on the spot!

25:50.400 --> 25:51.200
Your Majesty!

25:51.310 --> 25:52.070
Your Majesty!

25:52.070 --> 25:52.550
Consort Dowager An!

25:52.550 --> 25:53.350
Your Majesty!

25:53.640 --> 25:55.350
Shu is still inside!

25:55.510 --> 25:56.550
Shu!

25:56.790 --> 25:57.510
Consort Dowager An!

25:57.370 --> 25:58.510
[Qingyuan Palace]

25:57.680 --> 25:58.310
Shu!

25:58.310 --> 25:59.440
Consort Dowager An!

25:59.550 --> 26:01.030
Why are you stopping me?

26:01.030 --> 26:02.440
Go save her!

26:02.440 --> 26:04.270
Save her!

26:04.830 --> 26:06.830
The Princess Royal is still inside?

26:06.880 --> 26:07.640
Why are you just standing here?

26:07.640 --> 26:08.720
Go put out the fire!

26:08.720 --> 26:09.200
Yes!

26:09.200 --> 26:10.160
Go!

26:10.790 --> 26:11.400
Shu!

26:11.680 --> 26:12.720
-Your Highness!
-Consort Dowager An!

26:12.720 --> 26:13.570
Consort Dowager An!

26:13.570 --> 26:14.310
Consort Dowager An!

26:14.150 --> 26:17.230
[Qingyuan Palace]

26:14.310 --> 26:16.750
The fire is too big!
You can't go in there yourself!

26:16.750 --> 26:18.160
Consort Dowager An, you must take care

26:18.160 --> 26:19.070
of yourself, Consort Dowager.

26:19.070 --> 26:21.200
Enough talking! I'll go in to save her!

26:22.310 --> 26:22.920
Wait!

26:23.790 --> 26:24.550
Gongsun Yin!

26:24.550 --> 26:26.000
-Shut up!
-I knew it...

26:26.070 --> 26:27.000
And you!

26:27.830 --> 26:29.490
You dare address me like that?

26:30.480 --> 26:32.920
[Qingyuan Palace]

26:36.670 --> 26:39.710
[Qingyuan Palace]

26:43.480 --> 26:44.280
Your Majesty,

26:44.640 --> 26:45.860
once this news gets out,

26:45.860 --> 26:47.790
I fear the Yanzhou Army
under the Marquis of Wu'an

26:47.790 --> 26:48.920
will become unstable.

26:48.920 --> 26:49.790
And

26:49.790 --> 26:52.520
the Flower-Crowned General
who left early...

26:52.680 --> 26:53.830
Her Jizhou Army

26:53.830 --> 26:55.720
must also be addressed promptly!

26:55.720 --> 26:58.050
Then, Grand Tutor Li, what do you propose?

26:58.400 --> 27:01.860
I ask Your Majesty to grant me
full authority over this matter!

27:02.610 --> 27:03.590
Shu...

27:06.200 --> 27:07.960
Once that group of soldiers passes,

27:07.960 --> 27:09.560
we'll run into the corridor.

27:13.440 --> 27:14.570
Stay still.

27:19.510 --> 27:20.770
Changyu...

27:22.440 --> 27:24.060
I like you.

27:25.160 --> 27:26.220
Someone's coming.

27:39.480 --> 27:41.110
I really like you.

27:41.110 --> 27:42.630
Would you stop that?

28:04.960 --> 28:05.800
Who's there?

28:08.920 --> 28:10.680
He's there. After him!

28:12.960 --> 28:14.110
Stop!

28:21.070 --> 28:22.270
At a time like this...

28:58.480 --> 28:59.270
Shu!

29:00.200 --> 29:00.830
Shu!

29:01.680 --> 29:03.240
Your Highness the Princess Royal!

29:03.240 --> 29:03.880
Shu!

29:04.750 --> 29:05.610
Your Highness.

29:05.920 --> 29:07.180
-Shu.
-Your Highness.

29:09.970 --> 29:12.350
[Qingyuan Palace]

29:11.590 --> 29:13.550
Shu... Shu isn't breathing!

29:13.550 --> 29:16.270
She... She's not breathing! Shu!

29:16.270 --> 29:18.070
Quick! Summon the royal physicians.

29:18.070 --> 29:18.880
Summon the royal physicians!

29:18.720 --> 29:20.100
[Qingyuan Palace]

29:18.880 --> 29:19.400
Yes!

29:22.790 --> 29:23.690
Shu!

29:24.270 --> 29:25.830
The Princess Royal is a witness.

29:25.830 --> 29:27.200
If she lives,

29:27.310 --> 29:29.790
Xie Zheng will still have a chance
to turn things around.

29:29.790 --> 29:31.160
Whoever set this fire

29:31.310 --> 29:33.240
is truly ruthless.

29:39.310 --> 29:40.310
She's breathing.

29:40.510 --> 29:41.510
She's breathing!

29:50.000 --> 29:50.720
Gongsun Yin!

29:50.720 --> 29:52.550
You're defiling the Princess Royal,

29:50.820 --> 29:54.440
[Qingyuan Palace]

29:52.550 --> 29:54.720
denying her even the peace of death!

29:55.720 --> 29:56.780
What are you doing?

29:56.790 --> 29:57.480
Consort Dowager An,

29:57.480 --> 29:58.310
someone taught me this.

29:58.310 --> 29:59.750
This method can save her.

29:59.750 --> 30:00.960
Let me ask you: what matters more now,

30:00.960 --> 30:02.490
her reputation or her life?

30:02.600 --> 30:03.190
You...

30:05.310 --> 30:06.960
Save her. Save her now!

30:08.770 --> 30:12.810
[Qingyuan Palace]

30:08.920 --> 30:09.480
Well...

30:22.350 --> 30:23.280
Your Majesty...

30:24.350 --> 30:26.010
H-How dare you!

30:26.200 --> 30:27.550
This is outrageous!

30:27.840 --> 30:29.830
Humiliating the Princess Royal in public—

30:29.830 --> 30:31.240
have you no regard
for the royal family's dignity?

30:31.240 --> 30:31.960
Indeed.

30:31.960 --> 30:33.550
Guards! Seize him!

30:34.790 --> 30:36.190
I'd like to see who dares!

30:38.070 --> 30:40.750
In the first half of my life,
I spilled too much blood.

30:40.750 --> 30:42.370
Only in my later years,
through prayer and penance,

30:42.370 --> 30:44.410
did I manage to preserve my only daughter!

30:44.240 --> 30:47.770
[Qingyuan Palace]

30:45.400 --> 30:47.680
If I can't even preserve Shu'er's life,

30:48.000 --> 30:50.040
I don't mind killing a few more!

30:52.480 --> 30:54.420
Commanders of the Imperial Guards—
heed my order!

30:54.240 --> 30:59.870
[Qingyuan Palace]

30:54.480 --> 30:55.440
-Yes, Your Highness!
-Yes, Your Highness!

30:55.440 --> 30:57.110
Seal all exits.

30:57.400 --> 31:00.000
If a single word of tonight's events
leaks out,

31:00.110 --> 31:02.310
everyone present, without exception,

31:02.680 --> 31:04.110
shall die!

31:04.300 --> 31:05.480
-Yes, Your Highness!
-Yes, Your Highness!

31:04.380 --> 31:07.500
[Qingyuan Palace]

31:06.960 --> 31:07.680
Follow me!

31:08.310 --> 31:10.110
L-Listen to Consort Dowager An.

31:10.830 --> 31:11.880
We'll do as Consort Dowager An says.

31:11.880 --> 31:12.920
Gongsun,

31:12.920 --> 31:14.880
I order you to save her.

31:15.350 --> 31:16.920
If you cannot save Shu,

31:16.920 --> 31:18.070
you will die too!

31:26.910 --> 31:29.940
[Qingyuan Palace]

31:32.310 --> 31:33.240
Shu!

31:37.440 --> 31:37.960
Shu!

31:37.960 --> 31:38.760
You're awake.

31:39.160 --> 31:40.590
Shu, you're awake!

31:42.590 --> 31:43.240
Shu!

31:43.240 --> 31:44.040
Your Majesty,

31:44.590 --> 31:47.510
although Gongsun Yin
saved the Princess Royal,

31:47.510 --> 31:48.750
that does not prove

31:48.750 --> 31:50.310
Xie Zheng's innocence!

31:50.310 --> 31:51.840
Whether he is an accomplice

31:51.920 --> 31:55.480
can only be determined
after interrogation.

31:57.110 --> 31:57.880
Well...

31:59.510 --> 32:01.640
The one who saved
the Princess Royal tonight

32:01.640 --> 32:03.070
was a royal physician.

32:03.720 --> 32:05.900
Gongsun was never here.

32:11.400 --> 32:13.200
What do you think, Your Highness?

32:13.200 --> 32:14.030
Precisely.

32:14.440 --> 32:15.440
Tonight's events

32:15.720 --> 32:16.920
end here.

32:18.110 --> 32:18.850
Right.

32:19.160 --> 32:20.100
They end here.

32:20.880 --> 32:22.410
Tonight's events end here.

32:25.830 --> 32:26.960
Shu.

33:22.830 --> 33:23.550
Your Majesty,

33:23.550 --> 33:25.000
we haven't found the culprit yet.

33:25.000 --> 33:26.530
We've expanded the search.

33:27.350 --> 33:29.410
Are you looking for me, Your Majesty?

33:40.550 --> 33:41.550
The two of you...

33:44.640 --> 33:46.680
Why are the two of you together?

33:56.750 --> 33:59.110
And why are your clothes wet,
my dear subject?

33:59.110 --> 34:01.310
I was drunk and fell into the lotus pond.

34:02.350 --> 34:05.550
Fortunately, the Flower-Crowned General
pulled me out.

34:07.290 --> 34:08.060
Guards,

34:08.920 --> 34:11.230
bring the Marquis a change of clothes

34:11.400 --> 34:13.110
and prepare a bowl of ginger soup.

34:13.110 --> 34:13.550
Yes.

34:13.550 --> 34:14.550
Marquis of Wu'an!

34:15.230 --> 34:17.480
A fire broke out
in Qingyuan Palace tonight,

34:17.480 --> 34:19.400
and the Princess Royal
nearly lost her life!

34:19.400 --> 34:20.860
Witnesses have testified

34:20.880 --> 34:24.110
that it was all your doing—that you seized
a maid, defiled the imperial harem,

34:24.110 --> 34:26.310
and even tried to destroy the evidence!

34:26.320 --> 34:28.000
How do you explain that?

34:28.920 --> 34:31.520
I beg Your Majesty
to investigate thoroughly!

34:31.630 --> 34:34.330
The Marquis of Wu'an is the very culprit!

34:35.000 --> 34:35.320
You...

34:35.320 --> 34:36.280
I'm the culprit?

34:37.150 --> 34:40.480
Aren't you Imperial Guards out there
catching the culprit?

34:40.760 --> 34:43.280
What? Is there a second culprit now?

34:45.850 --> 34:48.310
Your Majesty,
the fugitive has been caught.

34:51.710 --> 34:52.510
Bring him in.

34:52.800 --> 34:53.440
Yes.

35:13.110 --> 35:14.480
Your Li family

35:14.960 --> 35:18.560
really put on a good show
of placing righteousness above family.

35:20.800 --> 35:22.190
How could it be you?

35:22.590 --> 35:26.070
I intended to confess my feelings
to the Princess Royal tonight.

35:26.070 --> 35:28.930
I never expected to
cause such a misunderstanding.

35:29.440 --> 35:31.300
And even disturbed Your Majesty.

35:31.800 --> 35:33.600
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

35:34.190 --> 35:34.880
Well...

35:35.000 --> 35:37.590
The one who went to see
the Princess Royal today was me—

35:37.590 --> 35:38.990
not the Marquis of Wu'an.

35:39.070 --> 35:41.070
Please judge wisely, Your Majesty.

35:46.510 --> 35:47.510
Why has this night

35:47.840 --> 35:51.700
been filled with so many
inappropriate acts and misunderstandings?

35:52.000 --> 35:54.110
I share Your Majesty's curiosity.

35:54.700 --> 35:56.560
I can usually hold my liquor well.

35:57.710 --> 35:58.960
I don't know why,

35:59.280 --> 36:01.740
but I got drunk
after just one drink tonight.

36:02.360 --> 36:04.680
Could it be
that the wine Your Majesty bestowed

36:04.680 --> 36:05.630
was too strong?

36:08.320 --> 36:11.600
That was the wine aged for a long time
in the palace cellars.

36:12.480 --> 36:14.340
Naturally, it was a bit stronger.

36:17.840 --> 36:18.760
The wine was...

36:19.280 --> 36:21.550
this servant, Li Xiang,
prepared it himself!

36:21.550 --> 36:22.190
Right?

36:22.880 --> 36:25.480
Could it be
you've harbored ulterior motives?

36:29.000 --> 36:29.590
I...

36:32.530 --> 36:33.380
Your Maj...

36:41.630 --> 36:42.760
That's right!

36:43.590 --> 36:44.600
This matter...

36:47.070 --> 36:51.840
was entirely my doing.

36:53.590 --> 36:54.590
It was all because

36:54.670 --> 36:58.160
the Marquis of Wu'an
had repeatedly humiliated me before.

36:59.440 --> 37:02.460
He even cut off one of my ears.

37:02.920 --> 37:03.760
So...

37:04.230 --> 37:07.190
So I harbored a deep grudge all this time

37:07.190 --> 37:08.880
and seized this opportunity

37:10.000 --> 37:14.070
to frame him.

37:14.550 --> 37:14.760
You...

37:14.760 --> 37:16.840
Was it also you who set the fire...

37:18.590 --> 37:20.390
in the Princess Royal's palace?

37:21.630 --> 37:22.280
Enough!

37:22.880 --> 37:24.480
You wretched slave,
you've betrayed His Majesty!

37:24.480 --> 37:26.840
His Majesty was also deceived

37:26.960 --> 37:28.120
by this servant!

37:32.320 --> 37:33.210
Your Majesty,

37:33.320 --> 37:35.510
it's clear that someone
set a trap tonight,

37:35.510 --> 37:37.910
trying to frame
the Marquis of Wu'an and me.

37:38.760 --> 37:40.140
I used to be a butcher.

37:40.230 --> 37:41.510
I don't understand grand principles.

37:41.510 --> 37:43.440
But I fought enemies on the border,

37:43.440 --> 37:45.170
surviving countless battles.

37:45.320 --> 37:46.390
Now that I'm home,

37:46.480 --> 37:48.480
I'm being framed by those around me!

37:48.480 --> 37:49.760
Perhaps Your Majesty,

37:50.440 --> 37:51.280
Grand Tutor,

37:53.230 --> 37:54.620
or Prime Minister Wei

37:55.590 --> 37:57.280
can explain this to me.

37:59.440 --> 38:01.100
The state is governed by laws.

38:01.360 --> 38:02.320
Li Xiang is guilty

38:02.320 --> 38:04.360
and will be punished according to the law.

38:04.360 --> 38:07.110
This has nothing to do with anyone else.

38:09.510 --> 38:10.310
Your Majesty.

38:11.000 --> 38:13.590
I wonder if the Longquan Sword
you bestowed upon me

38:13.590 --> 38:14.710
still holds.

38:26.030 --> 38:27.030
Of course it does.

38:39.880 --> 38:40.590
You...

38:42.710 --> 38:44.840
Since Your Majesty has granted me
the Longquan Sword,

38:44.840 --> 38:48.320
I shall rid Your Majesty of this traitor.

38:49.070 --> 38:50.470
Thank you, Your Majesty.

39:00.800 --> 39:01.840
My subjects,

39:02.550 --> 39:04.480
you're all the pillars of the state

39:04.880 --> 39:07.920
and have rendered great service.

39:08.960 --> 39:10.510
Regarding tonight's events,

39:10.510 --> 39:12.400
I will investigate thoroughly,

39:12.480 --> 39:13.920
root out the true culprit
behind this scheme,

39:13.920 --> 39:15.980
and see them punished without mercy.

39:18.800 --> 39:19.920
It's late.

39:21.230 --> 39:22.760
You may all take your leave.

39:27.230 --> 39:28.000
Let's go.

39:41.960 --> 39:42.760
Grandfather.

39:53.110 --> 39:54.080
Li Xiang...

40:03.800 --> 40:04.930
Prime Minister Wei,

40:05.150 --> 40:06.610
why haven't you gone home?

40:06.640 --> 40:14.040
[Speak with Caution]

40:09.400 --> 40:11.150
Seventeen years ago,

40:11.840 --> 40:14.300
the late Emperor
pulled the very same trick.

40:17.590 --> 40:19.030
You Qi family...

40:20.070 --> 40:22.000
you're all cut from the same cloth.

40:26.510 --> 40:27.110
You...

40:28.740 --> 40:30.540
This is the last time.

40:33.790 --> 40:41.010
[Speak with Caution]

40:39.840 --> 40:41.800
If it were the late emperor standing here,

40:41.800 --> 40:43.760
would you dare
treat him this way, Prime Minister?

40:43.630 --> 40:55.130
[Speak with Caution]

40:47.230 --> 40:48.890
Or has Your Majesty forgotten

40:49.480 --> 40:51.440
how you came to the throne?

41:36.440 --> 41:38.230
Such a deep gash.

41:39.360 --> 41:40.890
You should see a physician.

41:42.470 --> 41:45.870
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

41:46.580 --> 41:49.000
♪ The most beautiful scenery
becomes a poem ♪

41:49.630 --> 41:53.060
♪ For a chance encounter ♪

41:51.510 --> 41:52.570
What are you doing?

41:54.060 --> 41:57.910
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

41:58.300 --> 42:00.260
♪ I'll burn out my passion for you ♪

42:00.780 --> 42:04.430
♪ Just for a glance ♪

42:04.710 --> 42:05.470
♪ In this life ♪

42:05.490 --> 42:07.980
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

42:08.000 --> 42:09.700
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

42:10.140 --> 42:10.990
♪ On this journey ♪

42:11.020 --> 42:13.910
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

42:13.320 --> 42:14.230
Calm down.

42:14.020 --> 42:16.000
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

42:16.020 --> 42:16.870
♪ After we part ♪

42:16.890 --> 42:19.730
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

42:19.750 --> 42:22.050
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

42:22.080 --> 42:26.620
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

42:27.160 --> 42:31.290
♪ We'll never be apart ♪
